 It was definitely more impacted=E2=80=93=E2=80=93the team went from like 1=
5 to five people. It was the biggest ratio, but part of that was because th=
e way the team had been structured was much more old-school editorial, wher=
e it was all about these longform articles. We want to go more in the direc=
tion of having edit be integrated with social media, and they=E2=80=99ve be=
en very separate. The
goal is to merge the teams together so that when you think of Goop=E2=80=99=
s content, you don=E2=80=99t just think of long articles=E2=80=93=E2=80=93y=
ou think of a video where you saw the TL;DR version of the article, and the=
n there are tidbits that are cut for social so we have more of a presence t=
hat=E2=80=99s current. We=E2=80=99re also going to have more contributing e=
ditors who are more like the thought leaders in their space=E2=80=93=E2=80=
=93and that=E2=80=99s very Goopy.=C2=A0

The Focus Question
------------------

One of Goop=E2=80=99s biggest problems has been a lack of focus.
Going forward, what categories of the business are being prioritized?

=C2=A0

One of the things that we=E2=80=99re focusing on is G. Label, which is actu=
ally growing really well, despite the odds. We hired a new designer from Th=
e Row, and the second half of next year is when we=E2=80=99ll see her produ=
ct. It will be more colorful=E2=80=94Goopy=E2=80=94and there will be prints=
 and patterns. It will be more elevated. And there=E2=80=99ve been issues w=
ith
the fits=E2=80=94they haven=E2=80=99t been perfect, and it=E2=80=99s been a=
 little inconsistent. The reason that it=E2=80=99s doing well now is actual=
ly because they have taken an inventory position in a few styles, like thei=
r signature cardigan. It=E2=80=99s pretty expensive=E2=80=93=E2=80=93everyt=
hing=E2=80=99s made in Italy=E2=80=93=E2=80=93so we=E2=80=99re not increasi=
ng the prices. We are planning to try and participate in Fashion Week in so=
me way next year, and ideally, that=E2=80=99ll tie together the Goop world.=
=C2=A0

