y. Staudinger paid $78,000 for the Prada single-breasted black coat from 19=
97, $33,600 for a vintage faux-leopard fur coat (the flavor of coat is <a h=
ref=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJL=
